# =============================================================================
# mesha-frontend — Production Environment Defaults
# =============================================================================
# Committed NEXT_PUBLIC_* defaults for the production build.
# These are write-only Grafana Cloud ingestion credentials — safe to commit
# (same category as Sentry DSN: publicly visible in the browser bundle).
#
# Override any value in the Vercel dashboard or with a local .env.local file.
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OpenTelemetry → Grafana Cloud (prod-eu-central-0 stack)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
